468
00:21:17,166 --> 00:21:19,333
OH, SHOUKO, LISTEN.

469
00:21:19,416 --> 00:21:21,250
YUUJI FOUND OUT
THERE'S MORE TO HIM

470
00:21:21,333 --> 00:21:22,833
